#

### Install
```bash
pip install sfcparse
```

### Cloning the repository

Clone via HTTPS
```bash
git clone https://github.com/aaronater10/sfcparse.git
```

Clone via SSH
```bash
git clone git@github.com:aaronater10/sfcparse.git
```
